Welcome to Anastasiia Lavrenteva's Apps & Games! This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your personal information when you use our mobile game. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your data.
Information Collection and Use
Our game does not collect, store, or share any personal data from its users. We prioritize your privacy and ensure that your personal information remains secure and confidential.
Advertisements
The game includes third-party advertisements. These third-party ad networks may use technologies like cookies to collect information about your device and display relevant ads. We do not have access to or control over these cookies and their usage is subject to the privacy policies of the respective ad networks.
In-App Purchases
Our game offers in-app purchases to enhance your gaming experience. These transactions are processed by the app store you use (such as Google Play Store or Apple App Store) and are subject to their privacy policies. We do not collect or store any payment information.
Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
Contact Us
